titleInfo.title: Monaco v. Petco Animal Supplies Stores
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER OF DISMISSAL- The parties Amended Joint Stipulation for Dismissal with Prejudice (Filing No. 60) is approved, and the relief requested therein is granted; The Complaint and all claims in this action are dismissed with prejudice; Plaintiffs Motion to Define Testimony and/or Amendment of Pretrial Schedule (Filing No. 55) is denied as moot; The Clerk of the Court is directed to strike the parties Joint Stipulation for Dismissal with Prejudice (Filing No. 58) for the reason that it is an incomplete document; and The parties shall pay their own costs and attorneys fees. Ordered by Judge Laurie Smith Camp. (MKR)
